  <p style="font-size:14px;margin-bottom:0;"><strong>Who is most at risk:</strong> Anyone with pre-diabetes, insulin resistance, metabolic syndrome, type 2 diabetes, or family history of diabetes. The metabolic effects are dose-dependent and duration-dependent — longer use at higher doses compounds the risk.</p>
